reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Small, Easy to Use, and Performs.
reviews.reviewText: Fits fits right on my key ring and is hardly noticeable. When I need it, I can count on it to work.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for music in the car without allowing data mining of phone by auto manufacturers
reviews.reviewText: Instead of pairing my phone to my car and letting the auto manufactuerer mine my phone for sensitive information which they can and do sell, I now use this sweet little USB drive to take my music along when I drive. Sound quality is great and the car’s system has no problem whatsoever navigating the files in the drive. I’m fine with pulling over and parking to make a call and whoever calls me while I’m driving can leave a voice mail.Seriously, if you’re not already aware of how automobile manufacturers are data mining everything on phones paired to an automobile, do a web search on auto manufacturers collecting private data.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for recording music.
reviews.reviewText: Over the years I have recorded over 100 songs on my Pedal Steel Guitar. It is no longer practical to record them to CD or DVD. I put everything on these little thumb drives and label them with a small plastic tag label.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars One has died so far, with minimal use
reviews.reviewText: Grabbed these to add storage for our chromecast & firesticks. They seem to work fine in this use case. Nice form factor, the loop works great to put on a keychain or lanyard.I had a spare stick, which I started using to move some files in between laptops. after a dozen uses, the performance went to hell. File transfers taking longer and longer, eventually wanting 14 days to transfer 50 GB of files!I tried disc repair, reformatting in PC and Mac formats, nothing resolved the issue with this drive.Cheap junk, would not trust.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 19, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Much more durable, Security-conscious, and lightning fast
reviews.reviewText: I've been using "FireFly" model keychain thumbdrvies for years, because I liked that the drive came off the keychain from the bottom, and the cap stayed on the ring. I didn't like having to put my keys dangling from a drive, or have to hand someone my keys to let them put something on my drive.But, that's far outweighed by this one. It's not plastic, obviously, unlike most all the other modern thumbdrives.It works a bajillion times faster than the other one I had, too. I hadn't thought I notice that, but I do. I'm not worried about breaking this one and having to be careful with it, or constantly make sure that it's there and hasn't gotten broken off the keychain.AND - a big thing here - amongst several other keys, it doesn't draw attention to itself by LOOKING like a thumbdrive to tempt anyone to steal it if it's sitting alone for a few idle seconds. People steal keys just to get the thumbdrive all the time. But, this one is much more security conscious, because it's silver, and matches all of my other silver keys and rings. Most of the time I have to do a double-take just to make sure, because I don't notice it.12/10 would recommend. ;P

reviews.reviewTitle: Worked Fine for Two Years.... Until it Failed
reviews.reviewText: Used it sometimes every day for months at work. The small size was nice. It started to become very slow to transfer data. Eventually it stopped working all together. No amount of reformatting the drive made a difference. It was a cheap usb... but at the same time I've bought cheap usb's from Target that I still own... that are a decade old...
This is exactly what it says it is! This small storage drive is perfect for playing music from. It stays plugged into a light show device my child uses at night allowing it to play soothing music.
